Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description:
The period start date that the associated clause is written into the insurance product.

New and modified clauses etc. may be added over time and mailed to the customer as updates.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description:
The period end date that the associated clause is written into the insurance product.

New and modified clauses etc. may be added over time and mailed to the customer as updates.

Columns.Name: ProductClauseStatement
Columns.Description: The text of the associated Product Clause applied to the general Product.
